# Probability Question - Microsoft
### Question: a和b玩骰子，先擲到6的算贏，問a贏的概率
### My Answer: 

# 作圖
a - win (prob = 1/6)
  - lose (prob = 5/6) - win (1/6)
                      - lose (5/6) - win (1/6)
                                   - lose (5/6) - win (1/6)
                                                - lose (5/6) ...
故 a win probability = 1/6 + 1/6 * (5/6) + 1/6 * (5/6)^2 + 1/6 * (5/6)^3 + ...
無窮等比級數公式 a1 / (1 - r), 其中，a1 = 1/6, r = 5/6, 故答案 = 1
